bethlehem steel & lt ; bs > set plate price increa bethlehem steel corp said it base price for carbon plate and high-strength and low-alloy plate will be increa by 25 dlr to 405 dlr a short ton , effect juli one . the compani said it composit price for alloy plate will also be increa 25 dlr per ton on the same date , ad it doe not publish it price for thi product . bethlehem steel said it composit price for strip mill plate will be increa 15 dlr a ton .